{
  "_meta": {
    "currency": "AED",
    "units": "meters",
    "notes": "Edit these numbers to update the heatmap and the JSON exporter. Rooms use rate_per_m2 (multiplied by surface area). Doors/windows/columns use lump-sum cost per element. Lookup order: id -> subtype -> category -> default.",
    "room_finishes_notes": "Per-material/finish supply+install rates. Floor/wall/ceiling rates are AED per m2 of the relevant surface. SLAB rates are AED per m3 (multiplied by slab area * thickness). Join keys are the room user-text values: floor-finish, wall-finish, ceiling-material, slab-material. Lookup is case-insensitive; spaces, '-' and '_' are interchangeable. Falls back to 'default' when the material is missing or unknown. Rates only - no per-room totals."
  },

